Package: venv-analyzer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         python3,
         graphviz,
         sqlite3
Description: Python Virtual Environment Dependency Analyzer
 A GTK4-based tool for analyzing dependencies in Python
 virtual environments. Features include:
  * Visualization of package dependencies
  * Detection of conflicts
  * Size analysis of installed packages
  * Export capabilities for dependency graphs
